description:
Will The Great Reset bring global peace and prosperity? Or is it a great deception to bring in globalism and a new world order? Why is capitalism The Great Reset’s enemy? And how is spiritualism connected to the global social and economic restructuring process? Join TM hosts as they unravel the hidden truths behind the events in the headlines so that you can prepare for what’s coming. 

World leaders are saying that Covid-19 presents an opportunity to remodel society through what they’re calling The Great Reset, an opportunity to create a more inclusive and sustainable society. It sounds great, but for many who are paying attention to these things, there are aspects of this plan that are unsettling. Take, for example, the World Economic Forum’s video that tells us, “You will own nothing, but you will be happy.” And while some may nod with approval at talk of a universal basic income, others are not so eager to embrace government handouts for fear of what strings may be attached. 
What is The Great Reset? Why is it targeting capitalism as the enemy which must be removed, and quickly? How will the economic and social restructuring affect us? What kind of world are we heading for? And who’s behind it? 

This Truth Matters podcast takes a closer look at The Great Reset and shows that its ideologies predate Covid-19 by many years. Who are the people behind this plan to transform the world, and how are they connected? Professor Walter J. Veith, with cohosts Matthew Schanche and Mackenzie Drebit also delve into the history of the United Nations, which is guiding the global restructuring process, and reveal the surprising spiritual roots and connections of the organization.
